The [Spaces List Macro|https://confluence.atlassian.com/display/DOC/Spaces+List+Macro] lists all spaces, even if they are archived.  

Looking at our documentation and [the effect of archiving a space|https://confluence.atlassian.com/display/DOC/Archiving+a+Space#ArchivingaSpace-Theeffectofarchivingaspace], you will read: 

{quote}
In the space directory, the archived space will no longer appear in the general space lists.{quote}

